title: Ep. 1 - How did I get here?
itunes:title: Ep. 1 - How did I get here?
description: In an era that sometimes seems like never-ending doom, how can we find joy within each day? How can we decide what matters most? Every week, I'm going to share what makes me happy through this podcast. When it comes to content, I'm going to follow my heart, and I hope you'll come along with me!
